name: Rust-Oleum LeakSeal White Rubberized Spray
description: Rust-Oleum LeakSeal White Spray is an easy to use, rubberized protective utility coating designed to fill and seal leaks and cracks. It provides a water-tight, flexible seal that prevents moisture penetration, rust, and corrosion.
